title: Hot Numbers Coffee - Trumpington St
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Beer/Wine, Take-out, British, English, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Coffee roaster and cafe offering a small food menu. All the beer and a substantial proportion of the food options are vegan suitable and labeled. The daily soup is usually vegan and gluten free; the salad is available as a vegan meal; one panini is vegan. Typically the only baked item that's vegan is a flapjack-style bar with dried fruit on top. The breakfast menu is basic, with a few vegan-friendly choices (e.g. toast with jam, porridge with cinnamon and prunes).
